              <p>
                Beyond his PM work, Afolabi serves as Head of Programs &amp; Partnerships at GenZtechies,
                Africa's largest network for Gen Z techies, where he has organized hackathons attended
                by over 3,000 people. In 2025, he was named Rising Star Product Manager at The Dive Awards.
              </p>
              <p>
