        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-3" id="faq">
          {[
            {
              q: 'Do I need to know how to code?',
              a: "No. The workshop is designed for builders at all levels: developers, designers, PMs, and founders who've never written a line of code. AI tools handle the heavy lifting. What matters is how you think about the problem.",
            },
            {
